This paper deals with software security and vulnerability management, which falls under the software engineering (cs.SE) category. It also involves tracking and analyzing code repository issues and bug reports, which is related to computer security (cs.CR) and programming languages (cs.PL). The use of a security knowledge graph also involves data management and information retrieval (cs.SI). Overall, cs.SE is the most likely category, followed by cs.CR, cs.PL, cs.SI, and cs.SE.
